headline: CAN Community Health and Walgreens Partner for National HIV Testing Day
summary: TAMPA, Fla., June 24, 2025--On National HIV Testing Day, CAN Community Health is partnering with Walgreens to support the national ‘Greater Than HIV’ campaign. This initiative provides free, confidential HIV testing at Walgreens locations nationwide on Friday, June 27, 2025.

headline: Busy week for earnings: How investors are positioning
summary: Traders are eyeing a busy earnings week with FedEx (FDX), Carnival (CCL), Micron (MU), General Mills (GIS), and Walgreens (WBA) all set to report. Market Catalysts host Brad Smith breaks down how investors are positioning ahead of earnings. headline: Is Walgreens Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Walgreens has lagged behind the Nasdaq Composite over the past year, and analysts remain skeptical about the stock’s prospects.
